{"tid":1997162,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"愛國愛黨「10年保證」 - 李碧華","createTime":"2020-05-01T12:46:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-01T12:46:41.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"e4a50dde19b407fae28aee87419111bf285dae50","tid":1997162,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T12:46:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF/daily/article/20200501/20910035/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E7%25A2%25A7%25E8%258F%25AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200501%2F20910035%2F&d=29ui5Tvv6aczeWgqk0vw1xR%2FdSTUI%2FcOXZwDwNjmD8Q%3D&h=d7b2fc39\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E7%25A2%25A7%25E8%258F%25AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200501%2F20910035%2F&h=76aa6a9d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF/daily/article/20200501/20910035/</a><br />\n<br />\n愛國愛黨「10年保證」 - 李碧華<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20200501/large/1588238002_36f5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20200501%2Flarge%2F1588238002_36f5.jpg&h=292003d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大陸官方已通知各大影片平台及影視公司，盡量不用香港、台灣幕前幕後人員，若沒有表態是「愛國者」、「護旗手」，更加不獲聘用。為配合官方嚴苛打壓，在簽署買賣版權合約時增加一項條款，指明參加演出的港台藝人，須「保證10年內不會因政治取向遭大陸封殺，如有違約，影片平台有權追討賠償」。<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n「愛國愛黨愛人民（幣）」不是終身信仰嗎？怎麼會有「賞味期限」？門檻太低了！豈容港台偽人埋沒良知作出短期妥協來撈油水？應該永遠封關鎖國嚴禁文化藝術交流，一於自拍自看自娛自樂自洗腦，免煩！ <br />\n<br />\n李碧華<br />\n電郵 :mcwriter@appledaily.com"}]}